# Deny-default build context: ignore everything, then allow only what the
# Dockerfile builds from. Image contents are already pinned by the explicit
# COPY lines in Dockerfile; this keeps the context minimal and secure-by-default,
# and keeps the cache stable if we later move to a `COPY . .` (cargo-chef) layout.
*

# Workspace manifests
!Cargo.toml
!Cargo.lock

# Crates the Dockerfile compiles
!apps
!crates

# Re-exclude heavy/generated paths under the allowed dirs (last match wins)
**/target/
**/node_modules/
**/.bun/
